msgid "7. Mahāvagga"
msgstr "7. The Great Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 71. Bhāvanāsutta → bhāvanānuyuttasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.71:0.3"
msgid "71. Bhāvanāsutta"
msgstr "71. Committed to Development"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.71:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Bhāvanaṃ ananuyuttassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when a mendicant is not committed to development, they might "
"wish:"

msgctxt "an7.71:1.2"
msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr "‘If only my mind were freed from the defilements by not grasping!’ "

msgctxt "an7.71:1.3"
msgid "atha khvassa neva anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati."
msgstr "Even so, their mind is not freed from defilements by not grasping."

msgctxt "an7.71:1.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an7.71:1.5"
msgid "‘Abhāvitattā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "It’s because they’re undeveloped."

msgctxt "an7.71:1.6"
msgid "Kissa abhāvitattā?"
msgstr "Undeveloped in what?"

msgctxt "an7.71:1.7"
msgid ""
"Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ, "
"pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ, ariyassa "
"aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa."
msgstr ""
"The four kinds of mindfulness meditation, the four right efforts, the four "
"bases of psychic power, the five faculties, the five powers, the seven "
"awakening factors, and the noble eightfold path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.126"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.71:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni aṭṭha vā dasa vā dvādasa vā."
msgstr "Suppose there was a chicken with eight or ten or twelve eggs."

msgctxt "an7.71:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tānassu kukkuṭiyā na sammā adhisayitāni, na sammā pariseditāni, na sammā "
"paribhāvitāni."
msgstr "But she had not properly sat on them to keep them warm and incubated."

msgctxt "an7.71:2.3"
msgid "Kiñcāpi tassā kukkuṭiyā evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "Even if that chicken might wish:"

msgctxt "an7.71:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata me kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ "
"padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjeyyun’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘If only my chicks could break out of the eggshell with their claws and beak "
"and hatch safely!’"

msgctxt "an7.71:2.5"
msgid ""
"atha kho abhabbāva te kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā "
"aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjituṃ."
msgstr "Still they can’t break out and hatch safely."

msgctxt "an7.71:2.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an7.71:2.7"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni na sammā adhisayitāni, na sammā "
"pariseditāni, na sammā paribhāvitāni."
msgstr ""
"Because she has not properly sat on them to keep them warm and incubated."

msgctxt "an7.71:2.8"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanaṃ ananuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi "
"evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when a mendicant is not committed to development, they "
"might wish:"

msgctxt "an7.71:2.9"
msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr "‘If only my mind was freed from the defilements by not grasping!’ "

msgctxt "an7.71:2.10"
msgid "atha khvassa neva anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati."
msgstr "Even so, their mind is not freed from defilements by not grasping."

msgctxt "an7.71:2.11"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an7.71:2.12"
msgid "‘Abhāvitattā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "It’s because they’re undeveloped."

msgctxt "an7.71:2.13"
msgid "Kissa abhāvitattā?"
msgstr "Undeveloped in what?"

msgctxt "an7.71:2.14"
msgid ""
"Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ, "
"pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ, ariyassa "
